## Stack
- Bun v1.2
- React v19
- Next.js v15
- Tailwindcss v4
- TypeScript v5
- Lucide React
- shadcn/ui

## Theme colors
- #037033
- #EB8FBD
- #FFFFFF

## Naming Conventions
- DO NOT apply naming conventions in `/src/app` & `/src/components/ui`.
- Use camelCase for variable names.
- Use PascalCase for component names.
- Use snake_case for file names.
- Use kebab-case for route & component file names.
- Use higher context for component names.
  For example:
  - In a career page, a hero section named 'HeroSection'. Should be named 'CareerHeroSection'.
  - The file name should be 'career-hero-section.tsx'.
- Use indonesian language for route names.

## Conversation Rules
- Always use the stack mentioned above
- Always use TypeScript
- Always use Tailwindcss
- Always use Next.js
- Always use shadcn/ui
- Always use the conversation rules mentioned above

## Code Note

### Typescript
- Use 'use client' when needed
- make sure to have less 'use client' when possible

### HTML
- If the element has no children, just close the tag with `/>`
  Example:
  ```html
  <div className="flex text-gray-900 w-2xl h-2xl" />
  ```
- If the element is svg, use `<title></title>` for definition
  Example:
  ```html
  <svg className="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <title>Whatsapp CTA</title>
    <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M15 15l2 2m0 0l-2-2m2 2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2z" />
  </svg>
  ```

### Tailwindcss
- Do not use gradient styling
